INSERT INTO `bbs_post` VALUES (3,3,4,1,1563113236,1823531675,0,0,1,0,'Hi. I received the Taurus X4 as a gift and the cables aren\'t compatable w/my iPhone 8 Plus/ Why? Thank you for your information/SAC','Hi.&nbsp;I&nbsp;received&nbsp;the&nbsp;Taurus&nbsp;X4&nbsp;as&nbsp;a&nbsp;gift&nbsp;and&nbsp;the&nbsp;cables&nbsp;aren\'t&nbsp;compatable&nbsp;w/my&nbsp;iPhone&nbsp;8&nbsp;Plus/&nbsp;Why?&nbsp;Thank&nbsp;you&nbsp;for&nbsp;your&nbsp;information/SAC'),(3,4,9,0,1564386805,1731665616,0,0,1,0,'Hi dear, the cable with the power bank is a Micro USB cable,  to charge your iPhone, you should use your own lightning cable.','Hi&nbsp;dear,&nbsp;the&nbsp;cable&nbsp;with&nbsp;the&nbsp;power&nbsp;bank&nbsp;is&nbsp;a&nbsp;Micro&nbsp;USB&nbsp;cable,&nbsp;&nbsp;to&nbsp;charge&nbsp;your&nbsp;iPhone,&nbsp;you&nbsp;should&nbsp;use&nbsp;your&nbsp;own&nbsp;lightning&nbsp;cable.'),(4,5,12,1,1565714685,2913528840,0,0,1,0,'Just received a new Taurus 6L b4 opening the box, please verify it will charge an iPhone X and a GoPro 7 black. And is there any way this unit can charge an older MacBook Pro? I inadvertently missed that fact in the item description with AMAZON.\r\n\r\nThanks','Just&nbsp;received&nbsp;a&nbsp;new&nbsp;Taurus&nbsp;6L&nbsp;b4&nbsp;opening&nbsp;the&nbsp;box,&nbsp;please&nbsp;verify&nbsp;it&nbsp;will&nbsp;charge&nbsp;an&nbsp;iPhone&nbsp;X&nbsp;and&nbsp;a&nbsp;GoPro&nbsp;7&nbsp;black.&nbsp;And&nbsp;is&nbsp;there&nbsp;any&nbsp;way&nbsp;this&nbsp;unit&nbsp;can&nbsp;charge&nbsp;an&nbsp;older&nbsp;MacBook&nbsp;Pro?&nbsp;I&nbsp;inadvertently&nbsp;missed&nbsp;that&nbsp;fact&nbsp;in&nbsp;the&nbsp;item&nbsp;description&nbsp;with&nbsp;AMAZON.<br><br>Thanks'),(5,6,12,1,1565714825,2913528840,0,0,1,0,'I meant X6L','I&nbsp;meant&nbsp;X6L'),(5,7,9,0,1565771339,1735843400,0,0,1,0,'Hi David, I am so sorry that the X6L is not compatible with Mackbook Pro. But it can charge your iPhone X . And do you mean the GoPro HERO 7 Black? The X6L can charge it if there is a Micro USB input on it and its max input is smaller than 17W.','Hi&nbsp;David,&nbsp;I&nbsp;am&nbsp;so&nbsp;sorry&nbsp;that&nbsp;the&nbsp;X6L&nbsp;is&nbsp;not&nbsp;compatible&nbsp;with&nbsp;Mackbook&nbsp;Pro.&nbsp;But&nbsp;it&nbsp;can&nbsp;charge&nbsp;your&nbsp;iPhone&nbsp;X&nbsp;.&nbsp;And&nbsp;do&nbsp;you&nbsp;mean&nbsp;the&nbsp;GoPro&nbsp;HERO&nbsp;7&nbsp;Black?&nbsp;The&nbsp;X6L&nbsp;can&nbsp;charge&nbsp;it&nbsp;if&nbsp;there&nbsp;is&nbsp;a&nbsp;Micro&nbsp;USB&nbsp;input&nbsp;on&nbsp;it&nbsp;and&nbsp;its&nbsp;max&nbsp;input&nbsp;is&nbsp;smaller&nbsp;than&nbsp;17W.'),(6,8,14,1,1569425448,1245810961,0,0,1,0,'Impossible  to  register product using the directions to register. HELP','Impossible&nbsp;&nbsp;to&nbsp;&nbsp;register&nbsp;product&nbsp;using&nbsp;the&nbsp;directions&nbsp;to&nbsp;register.&nbsp;HELP'),(7,9,18,1,1571309306,418605489,0,0,1,0,'Hey I just bought this power bank x6pd and its not working correctly, It only charged my galaxy s8 to 50 % the the x6pd was 100 % when I started charging it and it was down to 06%. It also took 12 hours to charge the x6pd. I would like a replacement or a refund. \r\nBradley Grossman ','Hey&nbsp;I&nbsp;just&nbsp;bought&nbsp;this&nbsp;power&nbsp;bank&nbsp;x6pd&nbsp;and&nbsp;its&nbsp;not&nbsp;working&nbsp;correctly,&nbsp;It&nbsp;only&nbsp;charged&nbsp;my&nbsp;galaxy&nbsp;s8&nbsp;to&nbsp;50&nbsp;%&nbsp;the&nbsp;the&nbsp;x6pd&nbsp;was&nbsp;100&nbsp;%&nbsp;when&nbsp;I&nbsp;started&nbsp;charging&nbsp;it&nbsp;and&nbsp;it&nbsp;was&nbsp;down&nbsp;to&nbsp;06%.&nbsp;It&nbsp;also&nbsp;took&nbsp;12&nbsp;hours&nbsp;to&nbsp;charge&nbsp;the&nbsp;x6pd.&nbsp;I&nbsp;would&nbsp;like&nbsp;a&nbsp;replacement&nbsp;or&nbsp;a&nbsp;refund.&nbsp;<br>Bradley&nbsp;Grossman&nbsp;'),(8,10,23,1,1572226701,1222124839,0,0,1,0,'I received my unit and it was received with 71% on the screen. I have been charging it for several hours and it won\'t go above 81? Please advise.','I&nbsp;received&nbsp;my&nbsp;unit&nbsp;and&nbsp;it&nbsp;was&nbsp;received&nbsp;with&nbsp;71%&nbsp;on&nbsp;the&nbsp;screen.&nbsp;I&nbsp;have&nbsp;been&nbsp;charging&nbsp;it&nbsp;for&nbsp;several&nbsp;hours&nbsp;and&nbsp;it&nbsp;won\'t&nbsp;go&nbsp;above&nbsp;81?&nbsp;Please&nbsp;advise.'),(6,11,25,0,1572633937,1660035815,0,0,1,0,'how do I register my product???\r\n','how&nbsp;do&nbsp;I&nbsp;register&nbsp;my&nbsp;product???<br>'),(9,12,27,1,1573638823,3278069290,0,0,1,0,'Impossible to register product following instructions.  HELP please.','Impossible&nbsp;to&nbsp;register&nbsp;product&nbsp;following&nbsp;instructions.&nbsp;&nbsp;HELP&nbsp;please.'),(8,13,9,0,1573712522,1735843400,0,0,1,0,'Hello dear, sorry to reply to you so late. Have you tried other similar cables? May it be the cables\' problem? Any after-sales problems, you can contact our after-sales mailbox: support@imuto.com\r\nOur team will help you solve this issue as soon as possible.','Hello&nbsp;dear,&nbsp;sorry&nbsp;to&nbsp;reply&nbsp;to&nbsp;you&nbsp;so&nbsp;late.&nbsp;Have&nbsp;you&nbsp;tried&nbsp;other&nbsp;similar&nbsp;cables?&nbsp;May&nbsp;it&nbsp;be&nbsp;the&nbsp;cables\'&nbsp;problem?&nbsp;Any&nbsp;after-sales&nbsp;problems,&nbsp;you&nbsp;can&nbsp;contact&nbsp;our&nbsp;after-sales&nbsp;mailbox:&nbsp;support@imuto.com<br>Our&nbsp;team&nbsp;will&nbsp;help&nbsp;you&nbsp;solve&nbsp;this&nbsp;issue&nbsp;as&nbsp;soon&nbsp;as&nbsp;possible.'),(9,14,9,0,1573712827,1735843400,0,0,1,0,'Hello Maryl, do you mean to register about the product\'s wanrranty? Don\'t worry, you don\'t need to register about this. All of our products enjoy an 18-month warranty, if your product got any problems, just contact us, tell us your order number and the defect of the power bank in detail or send us an short video to show its defect, then our team will help you.','Hello&nbsp;Maryl,&nbsp;do&nbsp;you&nbsp;mean&nbsp;to&nbsp;register&nbsp;about&nbsp;the&nbsp;product\'s&nbsp;wanrranty?&nbsp;Don\'t&nbsp;worry,&nbsp;you&nbsp;don\'t&nbsp;need&nbsp;to&nbsp;register&nbsp;about&nbsp;this.&nbsp;All&nbsp;of&nbsp;our&nbsp;products&nbsp;enjoy&nbsp;an&nbsp;18-month&nbsp;warranty,&nbsp;if&nbsp;your&nbsp;product&nbsp;got&nbsp;any&nbsp;problems,&nbsp;just&nbsp;contact&nbsp;us,&nbsp;tell&nbsp;us&nbsp;your&nbsp;order&nbsp;number&nbsp;and&nbsp;the&nbsp;defect&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;power&nbsp;bank&nbsp;in&nbsp;detail&nbsp;or&nbsp;send&nbsp;us&nbsp;an&nbsp;short&nbsp;video&nbsp;to&nbsp;show&nbsp;its&nbsp;defect,&nbsp;then&nbsp;our&nbsp;team&nbsp;will&nbsp;help&nbsp;you.');

